b)$200,000 on or before November 30, 2024, contingent upon Wildflower Foundation’scertification of $200,000 in additional commitments as well as Foundation staff review ofany required reporting and determination of satisfactory progress."', '7 Water Street  Boston, MA 02109', 'Yes - Final report due 4/30/2024', 'https://drive.google.com/open?id=1zVVZGVMLlKpbndpJvIhbHQ782JD2xCBP', 'Foundation General (default all National funds)', 'Arrived via ACH on 12/13/24', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'erica.cantoni@wildflowerschools.org', 'Erica Cantoni', 200000.00, DATE '2024-12-20', NULL, '7', 'Water Street  Boston', 'MA', '02109', NULL, TRUE, DATE '2024-04-30', NULL),
